OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FProtesters have been gathering outside
OL,7,Fthe former home of a Coronation Street
OL,8,Fstar following false rumours that the
OL,9,Fproperty would be used to house
OL,10,Fimmigrants.
OL,12,FThe #1.5m mansion in Heywood,
OL,13,Fpreviously owned by Julie Goodyear -
OL,14,Fwho played Bet Lynch in the ITV Soap -
OL,15,Fhas been surrounded by protesters
OL,16,Fafter claims the property would become
OL,17,Fa house in multiple occupation (HMO).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
