CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FRochdale council has confirmed no
OL,7,Fofficial plans have been tabled to
OL,8,Fcreate a HMO at Primrose Hill Farm,
OL,9,Fbut building work has begun at the
OL,10,Fsite without permission.
OL,12,FIt came after building work began at
OL,13,FPrimrose Hill Farm without planning
OL,14,Fpermission, and Rochdale council has
OL,15,Fconfirmed no official plans have been
OL,16,Ftabled to create a HMO at the site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
