OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FThe last official request for planning
OL,7,Fpermission came from Julie Goodyear
OL,8,Fherself, when she asked to fill in an
OL,9,Fall-weather exercise arena, which was
OL,10,Frefused in 2006.
OL,12,FThe confusion over the plans is
OL,13,Fbecause the application came through
OL,14,Fbuilding control, rather than the
OL,15,Fplanning permission section. Building
OL,16,Fcontrol applications look at how the
OL,17,Fdevelopment is constructed; whereas
OL,18,Fplanning permission outlines what is
OL,19,Fbeing built.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FEven if this application was approved,
OL,7,Fthe developer would still need
OL,8,Fplanning permission before any
OL,9,Fbuilding work could start.
OL,11,FActivists from the Heywood Community
OL,12,FGuard and Heywood HMO protesters
OL,13,FFacebook groups have vowed to continue
OL,14,Fprotesting each weekend until they get
OL,15,Fconfirmation there will be no HMO on
OL,16,Fthe site. Posts in these groups have
OL,17,Ffalsely claimed there are plans to use
OL,18,Fthis site to house immigrants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FThere has been no mention of
OL,7,Fimmigrants being housed at the site
OL,8,Fincluded in plans publicly available
OL,9,Fon the council website.
OL,11,FA building control application for a
OL,12,F15-bed HMO was submitted to the
OL,13,Fcouncil in October 2025, but this was
OL,14,Famended to become a 15-bedroom bed and
OL,15,Fbreakfast in November 2025.
OL,17,FThere was an attempted application
OL,18,Fmade in February 2026 to build 10 two-
OL,19,Fbedroom apartments and to convert the
OL,20,Fstables into a three-bedroom house.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FRochdale council confirmed the
OL,7,Fapplication was not valid due to a
OL,8,Flack of detail ` so it was never
OL,9,Fpublished on the council's planning
OL,10,Fportal.
OL,12,FDespite no permission for any form of
OL,13,Fbuilding work being granted, work did
OL,14,Fstart on the former home of the Corrie
OL,15,Ficon. The local authority issued a
OL,16,Ftemporary stop notice (TSN) on 20
OL,17,FFebruary, after being alerted to the
OL,18,Fstart of construction work by local
OL,19,Fcouncillors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FLocal ward councillor, Paul O'Neill,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We just have to stop this
OL,8,Fdisinformation about this site and
OL,9,Fother sites. There is no planning
OL,10,Fpermission for this property and
OL,11,Fbuilding work has been stopped
OL,12,Ffollowing concerns raised by residents
OL,13,Fand councillors.
OL,15,F"Residents quite rightly were
OL,16,Fconcerned about it and now planning
OL,17,Fenforcement action has taken action."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
