PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Rochdale council
OL,7,Fsaid: "The individual concerned did
OL,8,Fsubmit a planning application to us
OL,9,Fsome weeks ago, but this application
OL,10,Fwas for nine dwellings, not an HMO.
OL,12,F"This application wasn't valid, so is
OL,13,Fnot listed on our website, as would be
OL,14,Fthe case with any invalid application.
OL,15,FAn invalid application is one where
OL,16,Fthe applicant hasn't submitted enough
OL,17,Finformation to enable officers to make
OL,18,Fa recommendation on whether the
OL,19,Fapplication should be approved or not.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
