PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773252372
OL,3,CProtests at Corrie star's old house
OL,4,Cafter false immigrant housing rumours
OL,6,F"Regarding the reported building on
OL,7,Fsite without planning permission, the
OL,8,Ftemporary stop notice remains in place
OL,9,Fand our enforcement team are making
OL,10,Fregular visits to the site and
OL,11,Fspeaking to residents in neighbouring
OL,12,Fproperties to ensure that the
OL,13,Findividual concerned is complying with
OL,14,Fthis temporary stop notice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@\O]
